 be 5000 kilograms for this atomic rocket reactor.<br>
<br>
3.Use water (H2O) as both the propellant, and the moderator.<br>
<br>
4. This reactor requires water in its core to sustain<br>
a fission reaction. Without the water the reaction ends,<br>
naturally because the neutron multiplier factor is to<br>
low in the atomic core with out the water.<br>
<br>
5.The core contains only 50 kilograms of U 235 <br>
contained inside of 4950 kilograms of inert, and <br>
