running through it, and being spewed out the other end<br>
as a plasma of ionized hydrogen,and oxygen gas.<br>
<br>
7. If the reactor crashes no radioactive materiaL<br>
will be scattered, because it is all trapped inside of<br>
 an inert lump of 5000 kilograms of solid Uranium  metal<br>
that is sheated in an inner casing of beryllium metal,<br>
 and an outer casing of titanium metal.<br>
<br>
