of this atomic engine  would be  about 600 seconds.<br>
<br>
9. Si = 600 seconds however is enough to enable 1 stage to leo with a 5/1 mass ratio.The vehicle would<br>
be a reusable delta winged nuclear rocket propelled 1 stage space plane.<br>
<br>
10. How is this for a safe , and ground launched ntr system.<br>
